nista team\u0026#39;s true (#notspon) fashion and \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/beauty\"\u003ebeauty\u003c/a\u003e obsessions, handpicked by professionals who see it all.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpring seems to finally be spring-ing, and I\u0026#39;m turning my attention to my warm-weather wardrobe. I typically focus on the basics: a \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/2025/04/apiece-apart-alessandra-sarong-shirt-dress-review\"\u003eversatile, lightweight dress\u003c/a\u003e; a good pair of jorts; some cute, comfortable sandals. But a few joyful, perfectly summery accessories have also caught my eye recently. Hair-care brand Crown Affair partnered with \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/jewelry\"\u003ejewelry\u003c/a\u003e and clothing label Éliou to create what I\u0026#39;m going to prematurely deem the must-have accessories of summer 2025.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe collab includes Crown Affair\u0026#39;s signature green silk \u003ca href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-16342571\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003escrunchie\u003c/a\u003e, leveled up with a collection of natural freshwater pearl pendants, and a green satin-corded beaded statement \u003ca href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-16342602\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003enecklace\u003c/a\u003e. Both of them can be worn multiple ways, ideally beachside, all summer long.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1197px) 1197px, calc(50vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:101%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_190/MjE0MjcwNjQ5Mjc3ODgzNDE1/crown-affair-eliou-scrunchie.webp 190w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:101%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw